This paper discusses the use of correlation in information retrieval, which is a key topic in the sub-field of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of quantum mechanics concepts such as entanglement, which is related to the sub-field of Quantum Physics (cs.QU). The paper also discusses the use of novel association methods, which is related to the sub-field of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of experimental testing, which is related to the sub-field of Machine Learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the fusion of different modalities, which is related to the sub-field of Multimedia (cs.MM).
